msgSnippet: Greetings! A new site of projects/bids has been opened recently: http://www.RainbowJ.com If you are owner of software company or freelancer this site may help
messageBody:
Greetings!
A new site of projects/bids has been opened recently:
http://www.RainbowJ.com

If you are owner of software company or freelancer this site may help you to find new customers!

You can register for free, create profile and upload your portfolio.
The site was launched just a few weeks ago and there are already several projects to bid.

If you have projects to be done, you can post them, it's absolutely free.

It's really great site.

Visit and try it:
http://www.RainbowJ.com
